<header class="page-title"><div><p class="eyebrow">GAME RULES</p><h1>How To Play</h1></div></header>
<section class="rules">
    <h2>Gomoku: Five in a Row</h2>
    <p>Players alternate placing markers on an empty board position. The first player to connect five markers horizontally, vertically or diagonally wins.</p>
    <div class="rules-grid">
        <div><strong>Board</strong><span>Choose 10 x 10 or 15 x 15.</span></div>
        <div><strong>Turn timer</strong><span>Each room defines thinking time.</span></div>
        <div><strong>Online</strong><span>Create a room, invite a player or add AI.</span></div>
        <div><strong>Replay</strong><span>Premium members review completed games.</span></div>
    </div>
</section>
